name: White Flag (for the Oceans) IV
description: The final artwork from the #CleanNFT series "White Flag for the Oceans" Video & Audio by Artist & Environmental Activist Carmen Danae Azor @carmendanae. The performance-art piece is a meditation on raising a white flag for the warming Oceans and all the species we've already lost to extinction due to anthropogenic causes. 100% of the sale & royalties will go towards Ocean Conservation & Climate Action projects in the Dominican Republic where the performance took place. 60seconds, 2880 × 2160
